==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: palm off
<hw>palm` off"</hw> <pr>(p⟦aum⟧m)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <sd>(a)</sd>
<cd>To dispose of fraudulently or deceptively; <as>as, to <ex>palm
off</ex> a counterfeit item as genuine</as>.</cd>
<specif>Hence:</specif> <sd>(b)</sd> <cd>To induce acceptance of
(something) by misrepresenting it as something better.</cd>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Palm Sunday</ent>⟦br⟧
